---
import { FREEPHONE_NUMBER } from '../../../../../utils/constants';

interface Props {
	location: string;
	locationTel: string;
}

const { location, locationTel } = Astro.props;
---

<h2 class="h3">
	Do you need a CCTV Drain Survey and live in {location} or the surrounding area?
</h2>
<h3 class="h4 coloured-text">
	Call us now on {
		locationTel ? locationTel : `Freephone ${FREEPHONE_NUMBER} - 24 hour Emergency Helpline`
	}
</h3>

<p>
	A CCTV camera survey is the <strong>quickest, easiest, and least destructive</strong> way to establish
	the cause and location of any drainage problem that is causing blockages.
</p>
<p></p>
<p>
	We have all the latest CCTV equipment which we use to determine what is causing the problems with
	your drainage system. Using this equipment means our local team of engineers covering {location} are
	able to perform <strong>quick "look-see" surveys</strong> or alternatively we can provide a more <strong
		>in depth service with full recording and report</strong
	>.
</p>
<p>
	We can ascertain exactly where the blockage or damage is and what is causing it. Knowing this
	means we aren't spending hours checking through all your pipe work and testing it and also means
	we know how to tackle the issue in the <strong>best and most cost-effective way</strong>.
</p>
<h3 class="h4">
	Call us today and find out why we're one of the highest rated companies for CCTV Drain Surveys in {
		location
	}.
</h3>
